data.description: Beautiful 3,347 sq ft, 5 Bedroom, 4 1/2 Bath Listing in the Beautiful Summerly Community. This home features a covered porch entry, elegant high ceiling foyer, 1 bedroom downstairs with a full on suite bathroom and walk-in closet, Dinning room, family room, then currently a mancave could be used as a den/office/playroom! and another 1/2 bath. The gorgeous well appointed kitchen, large granite island that seats at least 6, pendent and recessed lighting, stainless steel appliances, dark wood cabinets, plenty of counter space, tile flooring, coffee bar, large walk-in pantry and tile flooring. The upstairs has a loft/bonus room, primary suite with large on suite bathroom, separate tub and shower and 2 separate sinks and counters and a large walk-in closet. 3 more bedrooms, one with a full ensuite bathroom, the other 2 bedrooms and a full bath, large laundry room. There are custom Plantation shutters on practically all windows. The Dinning room has sliders leading to the very comfortable California Patio. The backyard is unfinished it has concrete walks, curbing and a unfinished fire pit area, BBQ area, concrete walks on both sides of the home, could easily be completed with artificial grass, sand pits for the kids just imagine it... there are leased solar panels. Tankless water heater, a water softener system. The Summerly Community offers pools, spa, clubhouse, various courts, parks, walking/running trails. golf course. Neighborhood is located near shopping centers, restaurants, Storm Stadium and easy access to freeway.
